import { makeStyles } from "@mui/styles";

const RegisterStyle = makeStyles({
    Box : {
        margin: "0",
        padding: "0",
        height: "600px",
        width: "350px",

        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "column",
        justifyContent: "center",
        alignItems: "center",
        border: "solid",
        gap: "2rem",
        borderRadius: "30px",
        userSelect: "none",
    },
    Input : {
        width: "75%",
        height: "25px",
        background: "#e0dede",
        justifyContent: "center",
        display: "flex",
        padding: "10px",
        border: "none",
        outline: "none",
        borderRadius: "5px",
    }
})

export default RegisterStyle
